metadata.description:
Suddenly, in a room lined with neat rows of servers, one server's indicator lights started flashing in a cold technological fashion. A blue flash of electric arc came out of the server, and suddenly it exploded, and there were no bones, and there was electric fire, and soon, every server in the room was destroyed.



End of screen.
